OL,3,CWATCH: Shane Lowry makes hole-in-one
OL,4,Cat The Masters
OL,6,FHole-in-one specialist Shane Lowry
OL,7,Fhailed his "wild" ace at the Masters
OL,8,Fwhich helped put him in contention
OL,9,Fheading into the final day.
OL,11,FThe Irishman has quite the collection
OL,12,Fof ones on his CV and this was his
OL,13,Fsecond at Augusta National, becoming
OL,14,Fthe first player to have that honour.
OL,16,FLowry's tee shot at the 190-yard sixth
OL,17,Fsaw him jump from six to eight under
OL,18,Fand he finished nine under after a 69,
OL,19,Fjust two off the lead.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@QO]
