PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776082266
OL,3,CWATCH: Shane Lowry makes hole-in-one
OL,4,Cat The Masters
OL,6,F"That's wild, isn't it? I made one a
OL,7,Fcouple of weeks ago in Houston. You
OL,8,Fdon't ever expect to make a hole-in-
OL,9,Fone, I just couldn't believe it," said
OL,10,Fthe former Open champion, whose
OL,11,Fprevious hole-in-one here came at the
OL,12,F16th in the final round of 2016.
OL,14,F"Obviously you're out there and you're
OL,15,Fin the hunt at the Masters and you're
OL,16,Fmaking hole-in-one, it's pretty cool.
OL,18,F"The walk down the sixth hole with
OL,19,Feveryone around 16 and the sixth was
OL,20,Fvery special. I'll remember that for a
OL,21,Fwhile. It was obviously amazing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]vD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
