PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776082266
OL,3,CWATCH: Shane Lowry makes hole-in-one
OL,4,Cat The Masters
OL,6,F"It gives you obviously a huge kind of
OL,7,Fboost. You go from six-under to eight-
OL,8,Funder and then all of a sudden you're
OL,9,Fonly four back.
OL,11,F"It's getting real now. I felt like I
OL,12,Fdid a great job of calming myself down
OL,13,Fafterwards."
OL,15,FLowry has also aced the 17th at
OL,16,FSawgrass, in 2022, and the seventh at
OL,17,FPebble Beach, in January 2025, two of
OL,18,Fthe most famous par threes in golf.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
